» Business Development Managger (offshore experience) – Grupo Norconsulting SL – Dubai Jobs
Posted on 29 April 2014. Tags: , , , , , , , ,
NORCONSULTING is a specialist company in the recruitment of top Energy & Oil and Gas professionals for our international and National Clients.
We are currently looking for one of our major clients in the oil and gas sector for a Business Development Manager. You would be located in Abu Dhabi/Sharjah
Brief on Role:
Responsible for Business Development of Upstream (offshore oil & gas projects) Sector in GCC countries 	like Qatar,
KSA,
Abu Dhabi,
Iraq etc across the Arabian Gulf.
Key competencies – Functional:
1.	Product knowledge / operational requirements2.	Client relationships3.	Business Understanding4.	Commercial / Contracting5.	Local knowledge 6.	Sponsor / Agent relationships 7.	Budgeting / MIS
Job Details
Date Posted:
2014-04-28
Job Location:
Dubai, United Arab Emirates
Job Role:
Sales
Company Industry:
Oil/Gas
Preferred Candidate
Career Level:
Management
